# Google Drive API
# Get a Client ID from https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 1. Create a new Google Cloud project
# 2. Enable Google Drive API
# 3. Create an OAuth 2.0 credential (type: Web application)
# 4. Add http://localhost:5173 to authorized JavaScript origins (for dev)
# 5. Add your deployed app URL to authorized JavaScript origins (for production)
# 6. Copy the Client ID below
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
